--- In nbwrpg@y..., "rAuq" <rauq@t...> wrote:
> Speedbreaker transforms, looking up at his friend, "Ummmmm, he 
> went to check on a Decepticon distress call" He then sees 
> Astroblast in the distance, "He's probably coming with Astroblast.
> 
> (Meanwhile)
> 
> Motormaster has found nothing useful, except for hatred. More 
> Autobots were now on earth, and that made him sick. He silently 
> flew up, away from the shuttle. He then spins aroung, holding his 
> gun out, and pulls the trigger, sending a wave of energy towards 
> the crashed shuttle. The burst hits it, and begins a chain reaction 
> of explosions, and all that is left behind where the shuttle was is 
a 
> crater, and a huge explosion. This brings a smile to Motormasters 
> fac but it leaves quickly. He starts to fly back to base, opening 
his 
> comm-link to the base, any robots in the presence of the base will 
> hear it. "I am returning to base, and will arrive shortly. 
Something 
> unfortunate has happened".
